SUB_W12_EVAR_DIVA_REMNANT_100_CUT_000_03.text:
Oh, but that's a proper shame;
I'll never find my heart in a world
that's frozen over like this.

SUB_W12_EVAR_DIVA_LEIA_100_CUT_000_040.text:
Oh, that was not a great challenge;
we mechs are fundamentally analytical
devices, after all.

SUB_W12_EVAR_DIVA_ICECASTLE_210_CUT_000_.text:
There is nothing for you here, traveler;
your mission lies elsewhere. There is no
cause for you to wager your life upon this.
